{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-b","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-learn-arrays-and-loops","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da biste pristupili elementima niza podataka, možete koristiti indeks broj. Indeksi počinju od 0, pa je prvi element niza podataka na indeksu 0, drugi element na indeksu 1, i tako dalje.</p>\n<p>Na primer, da biste dobili prvi element reda <code>fruits</code>, možete koristiti sledeći kod:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const fruits = ['apple', 'banana', 'orange'];\nconsole.log(fruits[0]); // Output: apple\nconsole.log(fruits[2]); // Output: orange\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ako je model van granica, JavaScript će vratiti <code>undefined</code>. To znači da ako pokušate da dobijete <code>fruits[3]</code> u navedenom primeru, će vratiti <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-learn-arrays-and-loops/learn-arrays-and-loops-lesson-b"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja je karakteristika koja se nalazi u četvrtom primeru reda <code>fruits</code>?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>orange</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>apple</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>pineapple</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>undefined</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Naučite o slojevima podataka i ciklusima treninga B","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-learn-arrays-and-loops","dashedName":"learn-arrays-and-loops-le